(i) any reference to the charge under section21B(1) is to be read as a reference to the charge under paragraph(h); (ii) any reference to the member is to be read as a reference to the spouse; and (iii) any reference to an encumbrance specified in section21B(3)(c) is to be read as a reference to an encumbrance referred to in paragraph(k);  (j) the charge under paragraph(h) is in addition to the charge referred to in paragraph(g), if the charge referred to in paragraph(g) continues to be in force; and
